{"tid":1326231,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"超合作運動 工程界 如何令新x機地盤注重環保安全","createTime":"2019-07-17T06:47:40.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-18T04:01:54.000Z","uid":277519,"like":67,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":28,"replies":[{"pid":"809263dca592bc10470752e12919c414ea69adb9","tid":1326231,"uid":277519,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T06:47:41.000Z","msg":"地產戰線一定唔會小得工程同地盤 <br />\n<br />\n新x基隨左有大量發長展項目亦有大部分承建商都係用返先自己公司。佢地係行內算係出名做得好，我地就幫佢做得更好，令到工人開心返工 安全收工。盡<br />\n<br />\n就例如<br />\n<br />\n1. 地盤出入口如發現清洗車胎不足令道路有泥積 1823環保署 會有告票<br />\n<br />\n2. 街外工程 ，包括任何行人路 或封緊路既工程有冇安裝好所有欄杆同燈 文件上有圖 同有冇合法既警方授權 （RMO 發出既RA) 同埋有冇路政署既excavation permit (路政署）張野有寫好時間地點大細 放係sorry 牌 冇跟足嫁話影低佢涉嫌非法封路及非法挖路。1823<br />\n<br />\n3.街外工程會有好多時攪到周圍都係泥，又或者放d架餐係街而又唔係本身合法既地方，方便開工。影低佢再來1823 阻街亂放野<br />\n<br />\n4.污水處理及塵埃，睇下地盤附近有冇水流出黎 一有泥水流出黎拍段片 環保署又隨時告得1823<br />\n<br />\n5.關注地盤工人安全 要帶安全帽及反光衣高空工作安全帶。多次唔載會罰錢甚至停工。住附近既不防高空拍片影落樓面會有好多有時工人唔載。勞工署 會派人黎1823<br />\n<br />\n6. 車輛地盤外違泊 停車唔熄匙 差佬過黎抄曬佢。仲要send比1823 運輸署投訴 阻礙交通咁先痛。<br />\n<br />\n7.地盤外好多時因爲地基攪到出面唔平 路面裂開 一黎會容易仆親人 二黎要防止地盤就沈降數據造假。我地要話比路政署知任何路面不平既地方 。<br />\n<br />\n簡單咁講工程進度慢左 就有機會要賠錢比業主 聲譽受損 用多左好多錢。但係我地注重環保安全工程。新記一定會同市民合作"},{"pid":"925151f930cf25f16db865523bafda833619320c","tid":1326231,"uid":277519,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T06:52:16.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"081c88426a146ad2f436322822b9d668f72c507f","tid":1326231,"uid":51701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T06:52:33.000Z","msg":"唔好推"},{"pid":"623f14ed800db3fdcf0b708b2953b0f5c83012a7","tid":1326231,"uid":277519,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T06:56:27.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"810db6816527cb71719fe8b854cbd1afbaec3c61","tid":1326231,"uid":51701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"623f14ed800db3fdcf0b708b2953b0f5c83012a7","tid":1326231,"uid":277519,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T06:56:27.000Z","msg":"Push"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T07:00:34.000Z","msg":"唔好推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6a453888e0d1a07b20c87c2ef6635663d46013fc","tid":1326231,"uid":258602,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T07:04:08.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"ee683c6c2c929e95bf8100d0bdbbaf7c912dcaec","tid":1326231,"uid":118125,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T07:22:30.000Z","msg":"基本上地盤實有安全問題<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">馬路</span><br />\n1. 地盤工程車輛違泊<br />\n2. 沒有權合法封路, 唔夠臨時路牌<br />\n基本馬路陣一定有緩衝空間比車輛抽出(類似Page 110 Fig. B-2)<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hyd.gov.hk/tc/publications_and_publicity/publications/technical_document/code_of_practice/doc/COP_201712.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hyd.gov.hk%2Ftc%2Fpublications_and_publicity%2Fpublications%2Ftechnical_document%2Fcode_of_practice%2Fdoc%2FCOP_201712.pdf&d=SosmRuku1xQpFtIKZJ5auRjXlokmAnOoGQHL1SEg040%3D&h=c9c1f5fb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hyd.gov.hk/tc/publications_and_publicity/publications/technical_document/code_of_practice/doc/COP_201712.pdf</a><br />\n3. 污水流出馬路旁的雨水渠<br />\n4. 環保斗(貨斗)擺放在街道或路旁一般不會超過兩至三天,至少一定有公司電話<br />\n(指引)環保斗必須漆上鮮黃色；公司名稱和電話號碼須標示於環保斗兩側；環保斗四邊須貼上紅白相間反光帶；晚上更需在環保斗四角附設黃色閃燈，或在周圍放置設黃色閃燈的交通圓椎桶。 <br />\n<a href=\"https://www.epd.gov.hk/epd/tc_chi/greenconstruction/aboutus/files/Mounting_Placing_ofskips.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.epd.gov.hk%2Fepd%2Ftc_chi%2Fgreenconstruction%2Faboutus%2Ffiles%2FMounting_Placing_ofskips.pdf&d=SosmRuku1xQpFtIKZJ5auRjXlokmAnOoGQHL1SEg040%3D&h=9fe7e13f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.epd.gov.hk/epd/tc_chi/greenconstruction/aboutus/files/Mounting_Placing_ofskips.pdf</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">行人路</span><br />\n1. 基本上大部份都係維持1.5米寬度, 視乎已批圖紙, 1.2至3.5米不等<br />\n2. 建築用料阻路<br />\n3. 建築廢料霸佔馬路/行人路<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">積水</span><br />\n任何容器有任何積水都可以投訴<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">高空工作</span><br />\n離地2米一定有合適工作平台, <br />\n佩帶安全帶, 扣上獨立救生繩 (基本上係無時無刻都有保護)<br />\n所有梯具只會供上落, 唔會用黎工作(只限簡易工作如換燈泡)"},{"pid":"297a387b42c1698f7c34cf4f825248e8b47639a3","tid":1326231,"uid":118125,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T07:32:06.000Z","msg":"1. D臨時路牌甩色睇唔清楚,影響行車行人安全<br />\n2. 工人清拆時,沒有眼罩耳塞保護 <br />\n第59I章 《建築地盤(安全)規例》<br />\n第509章 《職業安全及健康條例》<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>任何影響行人/道路使用者/工人自身安全</strong></span></span><br />\n記得1823投訴"},{"pid":"7a33a8815a8ec2a72ac87da09a797f9c3cc9319a","tid":1326231,"uid":277519,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T07:43:47.000Z","msg":"做野啦"},{"pid":"14e25b5263f5fb0bd153d175ec6f909dde539ede","tid":1326231,"uid":162910,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T07:44:22.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4d3c1d8359d2247aa21330c8eb38e6bf0d21eb02","tid":1326231,"uid":147620,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T07:49:21.000Z","msg":"啲工人出入食煙講粗唔著衫其實都可以投訴<br />\n一過左夜晚7點仲有燈/聲都可以投訴<br />\n發聽到少少聲覺得嘈又可以投資"},{"pid":"76080895d0aa2908a49df82f2398aa6ad873489a","tid":1326231,"uid":202621,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T07:51:22.000Z","msg":"工程<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"573aedd6bc4b955aee4b0c0db0521f8521aad3d5","tid":1326231,"uid":59898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T07:51:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f1906c3d31834d0f26cc00ed693b68f4e2982d5a","tid":1326231,"uid":10240,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T07:54:17.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"bc863528c39fb746f45373b4ba447582994e18e8","tid":1326231,"uid":160650,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T08:06:44.000Z","msg":"我冇嘢講"},{"pid":"c1e009d00d22c9389d80092517f7401097e42947","tid":1326231,